  {
    "function_v0": {
      "doc": "Configure the cross-chain bridge endpoint (admin only). This is the\\nfixed destination for record_bridge_out and source for\\nrecord_bridge_in \\xe2\\x80\\x94 the keeper never supplies an address, so it cannot\\ndivert funds. In production this is the vault-controlled remote-strategy\\nadapter; it should be set behind the multisig admin.\\n\\nRefuses to change the endpoint while funds are still recorded as out\\n(`bridged_balance > 0`): repointing mid-flight would strand those funds\\nat the old endpoint (record_bridge_in pulls from the new one). Recall\\neverything first, then migrate.",
      "name": "set_bridge_endpoint",
      "inputs": [
        {
          "doc": "",
          "name": "caller",
          "type_": "address"
        },
        {
